\cf2 Key design concepts:\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0\cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}P-Model\'a0= per-platform DRL model, trained on single-platform historical data\cf0 \
\ls1\ilvl0\cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}X-Model\'a0= cross-platform DRL model, trained on transformed/aggregated P-data\cf0 \
\ls1\ilvl0\cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}X-Execution drives P-Execution for each platform underneath\cf0 \
\ls1\ilvl0\cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Training parameters and execution parameters are separated\cf0 \
\ls1\ilvl0\cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}UI provides execution parameters; training uses historical data\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \
